message: "If you use this framework, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "Test Pilot Loop"
abstract: >-
  A multi-agent AI testing framework where AI agents test software through
  computer use — with different personas, knowledge tiers, and structured
  feedback loops. The AI test pilot operates your app through computer use
  (clicking, typing, navigating) and reports UX issues back to the build agent.
